metadata.description:
Stuffed Shirt Vasilia During Afternoon Ride With Her 1959 VW Beetle | 04:13 PM
.
Eagle Stop Gas Station, 
Where all the free souls are flitting the road and stay there for a while. No one knows the old school wheels better than the station and the pumpâ€”those who just dressed up like their ghosts.

Days after days throughout the years are passed away, and just the Eagle Stop Gas Station stays there and watches those free souls with all their stories and life, flitting and rushing the highway road!
